<plot>A classic &amp; lyrical love-tale with a bitter-sweet twist, I Heard the Mermaids Singing is a short-film adaptation of a play written by legendary acting coach &amp; casting director Michael Shurtleff who passed away January 28, 2007. I Heard the Mermaids Singing is an homage to him and his teachings which live on in our hearts &amp; minds.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?252471</url></doc>
